{
  "stem": "2316.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But otherwise, we didn't know because there was no communication.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was nobody to talk to.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Eventually, the partisans found us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But otherwise, we wouldn't have known when the war was over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "May be in time, I suppose, when we go out to steal food and bump into somebody or whatever.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Otherwise, we had no idea what's going on in the world.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, absolutely.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Except to venture out for food, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parents, my brother, a neighbor's child, who was two years older than I am-- who survived.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And two other friends of my parents.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One brother.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My older brother went to take care of cousins of mine in a different grave-- in a different cave, part of the woods, far away from us, because they were just girls-- cousins-- just girls.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they needed somebody else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he volunteered to go and take care of them and stay with them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were separated at the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe-- maybe once a month, once or two months-- very, very seldom, very seldom.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mostly maybe in the summertime a little bit outdoors a real tiny little fire because we were afraid of the smoke.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And were, you know-- You couldn't do that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But sometimes in the summer, when the leaves were in full bloom and it was noisy and the birds would and nobody could hear us, we would be far in the woods, we'd build our little fire, yes.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We would do that occasionally, but very, very seldom, very seldom.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had a little stove that we carried with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was just-- like I said before, we didn't have what to cook anyway.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So oh, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and believe or not, that after that, there were still a few people went back to, to the shtetl.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
